    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Grab your heroes</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702960/extras/481272382ac222d0627bab2446df68ce.poster.avif?t=1721659131\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702960/extras/481272382ac222d0627bab2446df68ce.webm?t=1721659131\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702960/extras/481272382ac222d0627bab2446df68ce.mp4?t=1721659131\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Indirect combat</h2>Prepare your heroes and let them fight on their own! Place stormtroopers in front, and snipers and stingers back. Equip your heroes with items to increase their characteristics or make them unique fighters.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702960/extras/f1f55c7c7b2cd7e89b1fdc1712c67371.poster.avif?t=1721659131\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702960/extras/f1f55c7c7b2cd7e89b1fdc1712c67371.webm?t=1721659131\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702960/extras/f1f55c7c7b2cd7e89b1fdc1712c67371.mp4?t=1721659131\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Endless exploration</h2>Dungeons are generated from scratch each time, and a new set of items is created for the heroes to use.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702960/extras/8243bc772ac334a51663d21bc7398c6f.poster.avif?t=1721659131\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702960/extras/8243bc772ac334a51663d21bc7398c6f.webm?t=1721659131\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702960/extras/8243bc772ac334a51663d21bc7398c6f.mp4?t=1721659131\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Death is not the end</h2>Some rare items after the death of a hero can transform him into something different, sometimes even more powerful and terrible ...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702960/extras/af164f30c86d4c9a06e10183e3fc8603.poster.avif?t=1721659131\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702960/extras/af164f30c86d4c9a06e10183e3fc8603.webm?t=1721659131\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702960/extras/af164f30c86d4c9a06e10183e3fc8603.mp4?t=1721659131\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
